      • PaneAdministrator

        public PaneAdministrator(Container container,
                 GridBagLayout layout)
        A constructor to create a new instantiation of the class.

        The adding of components to the GridBagLayout is handled via an instantiation of the GridBagConstraints class.

        Parameters:
        container - the Container to administrate
        layout - the GridBagLayout for the container
        See Also:
        GridBagConstraints
